1. *Upomoć* mi i pomoći mi da završim posao! (Help me to finish the job!)
2. Ona nam je pružila *upomoć* kada smo se nalazili u problemu. (She provided us with assistance when we were in trouble.)
3. Uvek možeš da računaš na moju *upomoć*. (You can always count on my help.) 
4. Da li možeš da mi daš *upomoć* sa učenjem? (Can you give me some help with studying?) 
5. Bez tvoje *upomoći* ne bih uspela da završim projekat. (Without your help I wouldn't have been able to finish the project.)